des:
This "Outfit ideas" skill helps you decide how to wear your clothes. It also helps you decide your outfit for any occasion, style or need you might have. 

- Alexa, give me ideas for my red jacket
- Alexa, search outfit ideas for a summer wedding with a red dress
- Alexa, give me outfit ideas for today

About: 
- This skill is your personal fashion stylist; 
- Helps you feel confident in your outfits; 
- You can create your digital closet, in seconds; 
- Each of your clothes will have ideas on how to wear them; 
- You'll also see how other real women wear the clothes you have, for any occasion, style or need.

How to get started:
- Download Chicisimo app for iOS or Android; 
- Easily and in seconds, create your digital closet; 
- Ask Alexa to show you how to wear your clothes.
